latestPosts.caption: The sounds of summer are calling our name.

What are Disulfide Bonds?
〰️ Disulfide bonds provide molecular-level structure to all hair types and textures.

Why are they important?
〰️ Strong bonds are vital to hair strength, elasticity and flexibility.

Discover how our OLAPLEX Complete Bond Technology™ is clinically proven to target and repair disulfide bonds, restoring hair’s strength and structure.
